review.reviewBody: Amazing quality and price! The food was incredible! Highly recommend! They should have 5 stars on this app!! I will happily order again
the sashimi was very good quality for how reasonable the price was. the portions were great and was better than expected for the price.

All good the tonkatsuwas good s but smaller than expected but was still
Good value for price maybe Ofer lager appy so
1/2 Abd 3-4 since it is an app. Salad good Abd Kia tentacles great

Flower Tartare was good but it would be better if they put it in different containers  it fell apart. But the House Roll 5pcs (招牌卷)was really good. Spicy Salmon Roll (8 pcs) (辣三文魚卷)was ok. Also didn't get any utensils hope they checked next time

Food used to be great here, then half a year ago or so the name of the place changed and quality dropped, prices also increased. I tried again recently wondering if the quality changed. This  was the only time i've thrown out nearly all of my sushi, and the last time i'll order from here.
